## Build Priority (from MASTER_PLAN.md)

### Phase 1 — Make it real (current focus)
1. Real auth (Section 1.1) — PostgreSQL + JWT + Google OAuth
2. Database (Section 1.2) — Alembic migrations, all tables
3. API wiring (Section 1.3) — /auth/*, /workspace/*, /threads/*, /artifacts/*
4. Multi-thread chat persistence (Section 8)
5. Onboarding v2 (Section 9)

### Phase 2 — Make agents complete
- 7 missing backend agent files (A8–A14)
- Workspace memory injection into every agent call
- Guardrail enforcement (validate thesis, ask before concluding)

### Phase 3 — Home screen live
- Widget system with live connector data
- Alert system fully wired

### Phase 4 — Artifact system
- Multi-session PRDs, artifact memory, publish flow

### Phase 5 — Workflow execution
- Workflow runner, trigger system, scheduler

---

## What's Working Right Now

- FastAPI backend running with 7 agents + LLM routing
- RAG pipeline (ingest, vector store, retriever)
- Jira connector: read ✅, create_issue ✅, comment ❌, update ❌
- /chat endpoint with intent detection + agent routing
- RBAC middleware + audit logging
- All frontend pages visually built
- Agent detail (6-tab config), Analytics page (6 tabs), Chat page

## Critical Gaps (Nothing else works properly without these)

- ❌ NO real auth — localStorage only
- ❌ NO database — no persistence for anything
- ❌ NO workspace memory injection — agents don't know company/product context
- ❌ NO artifact memory
- ❌ 7 agent backend files missing (A8–A14)
- ❌ Workflow is visual only — no execution engine

