## Key Files

```
onboarding/app/dashboard/
├── page.tsx                    # Home screen
├── agents/
│   ├── page.tsx                # Agent grid
│   └── [id]/page.tsx           # Agent detail (6 tabs)
├── chat/page.tsx               # Chat with thread sidebar + memory panel
├── analytics/page.tsx          # Analytics (6 tabs)
├── workflows/page.tsx          # Workflow builder (React Flow)
└── connectors/page.tsx

onboarding/lib/
├── platform-data.ts            # All agent defs, types, mock data
├── api.ts                      # All API calls — req() wrapper
└── auth.ts                     # JWT token store

backend/
├── main.py                     # FastAPI app + all routes
├── agents/base.py              # BaseAgent: RAG, context, governance
├── agents/strategy.py          # (and docs, analytics, ops, review, sprint, research)
├── connectors/jira.py          # Jira read + create_issue
└── rag/                        # Vector store, ingest, retriever
```

---

## DO NOT

- Do NOT use raw Tailwind colors (blue-500, etc.) — always use brand tokens
- Do NOT build PRD Copilot as a separate page — it's a mode within Docs Writer agent
- Do NOT add standalone "tool" pages — only agents, workflows, connectors, home screen
- Do NOT copy Clay/Perplexity/Dust UI literally — pmGPT has its own design language
- Do NOT add code editor, image gen, or non-PM features
- Do NOT make agents act without human approval on write actions (show preview first)
- Do NOT use emojis in the UI

